description:
Clay and Buck Sound Off H3 - The Best From This Week - Oct 23 2021


Sen. Blackburn calls for Dr. Fauci to be removed, discusses Merrick Garland's testimony on parents protesting critical race theory in schools, the border, the budget negotiations, NBA's Enes Kanter on China. Jim Jordan grills Merrick Garland. Hilarious clips from the Netflix transgender walkout. Biden: Build Back Better budget costs zero.
